# MemoBrain Integration - Frontend Project

## Project Isolation

**Project ID**: `frontend`
**Storage**: `_bmad-output/memory/frontend/`
**Required Tag**: `project:frontend`

## Quick Reference

```
SESSION ID:  frontend_{phase}_{agent}_{context}
STORAGE:     _bmad-output/memory/frontend/
REQUIRED:    project:frontend, phase:{phase}, agent:{name}
```

## MCP Commands

| Command | Frontend Usage |
|---------|---------------|
| `memory_init` | `session_id="frontend_{phase}_{agent}_{context}"` |
| `memory_store` | `tags=["project:frontend", ...]` |
| `memory_query` | `tag="project:frontend"` for isolation |
| `memory_save` | `filename="frontend/{context}_{agent}.json"` |

## Isolation Rules

- ✅ Always use `project:frontend` tag
- ✅ Save to `frontend/` subfolder
- ✅ Can read backend sessions (read-only)
- ❌ Never write to backend sessions

